  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-form\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-form/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 89 (B)\n**Known issues:** _styles, _handleSubmit, _handleReset missing descriptions.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_events`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Layout spacing. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Form landmark. Label associations. Error summary. Required fields.\n3. **Functionality** — Form submission (native + custom). Reset. Validation (constraint API). FormData collection from custom elements. Nested forms.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`. FormData typing.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Layout (vertical/horizontal). Spacing. CSS Parts.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Fix 3 missing descriptions.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Submit. Reset. Validation. FormData. Custom elements.\n8. **Storybook** — Simple form. Validation. Custom elements. Submit handling.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Drupal Form API. AJAX form submission. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready. Form-associated custom elements integration.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
